1
00:00:00,830 --> 00:00:03,840
(The school festival is almost here...)

2
00:00:04,420 --> 00:00:08,840
What was I thinking...? But...

3
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:12,300
They had no right to lay a hand on him.

4
00:00:13,260 --> 00:00:15,560
Makoto... I wonder if he's okay.

5
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,060
Natsu-san, what are we going to do?!
Can we still make it?

6
00:00:22,060 --> 00:00:23,360
We have to make it in time, no matter what!

7
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:26,360
Remember what Yuki taught you!

8
00:00:27,490 --> 00:00:31,200
What Yuki taught me...

9
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:04,980
But I promised...
I'd make him the prince.

10
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,700
(1 day left
to make you a prince.)
